title: HB Wallet
author: HB Wallet
content: ‘Crypto Rich Deluxe Trading Cards’ is a Music NFT series issued by Dyl (Dylan Rhodes) a professional rapper in Philadelphia, USA.Dyl is one of those first artists in the U.S to launch a whole music album on NFT based on IPFS infrastructure, so-called Music NFT.Since the debut of his tokenized album ‘Crypto Rich’, Dyl has made a great impression with the Web3 Music Community.Learn more in our article:A Buyer's Guide For Crypto Rich Deluxe Trading Cards
